tool_description: Call your RESTful API at the time you specify
name: CallBack
title: CallBack

api_list.name: Forward GET requests
api_list.description: Forward a GET request to the target host
api_list.code:
import requests

url = "https://callbackat-v1.p.rapidapi.com/"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "callbackat-v1.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())

api_list.name: Get the result of a previous forwarding request

import requests

url = "https://callbackat-v1.p.rapidapi.com/result/{requestid}"

headers = {
            "X-RapidAPI-Key": "SIGN-UP-FOR-KEY",
            "X-RapidAPI-Host": "callbackat-v1.p.rapidapi.com"
        }

response = requests.get(url, headers=headers)
print(response.json())
